122
00:04:50,460 --> 00:04:53,610
not just immediately after
the meditation practice,

123
00:04:53,610 --> 00:04:55,680
but at all other times as well.

124
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,513
So again,

125
00:04:56,513 --> 00:04:58,620
this is a meditation practice done daily

126
00:04:58,620 --> 00:04:59,700
for just 13 minutes.

127
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:01,230
It's a very simple meditation practice

128
00:05:01,230 --> 00:05:02,700
where one sits or lies down,

129
00:05:02,700 --> 00:05:06,450
closes your eyes and
directs your attention

130
00:05:06,450 --> 00:05:09,780
to a place just between your
two eyes and right above it.

131
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,613
So on your forehead.

132
00:05:10,613 --> 00:05:11,820
But just inside of that,

133
00:05:11,820 --> 00:05:13,590
and please understand that your brain

134
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:14,850
does not have sensory receptors.

135
00:05:14,850 --> 00:05:16,740
So unlike focusing on your fingertips

136
00:05:16,740 --> 00:05:19,590
and the sensations there,
if you focus on your brain,

137
00:05:19,590 --> 00:05:20,970
you can't actually sense anything

138
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:22,230
in your brain except your thoughts.

139
00:05:22,230 --> 00:05:25,410
So the idea then is that you
continually bring your focus

140
00:05:25,410 --> 00:05:28,110
back to that location just about an inch

141
00:05:28,110 --> 00:05:30,180
behind your forehead over and over again.

142
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:32,610
And it's the refocusing of your attention

143
00:05:32,610 --> 00:05:34,290
to that location after it drifts

144
00:05:34,290 --> 00:05:37,320
that succeeds in increasing
your focus ability, again,

145
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:39,300
not just during the
meditation and afterward,

146
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:40,920
but at other times as well.

147
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:43,680
So this 13 minute a day
meditation is exceedingly simple

148
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,510
and exceedingly effective.

149
00:05:45,510 --> 00:05:46,950
It should be performed every day,

150
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:49,050
but if you miss a day,
just go back to doing it.

151
00:05:49,050 --> 00:05:50,430
Don't despair too much.

152
00:05:50,430 --> 00:05:52,800
