Alpha GPC taken in 300
milligram form 10 to 30 minutes

198
00:07:38,820 --> 00:07:41,850
before a about of cognitive
work or a about of physical work

199
00:07:41,850 --> 00:07:44,760
will increase your focus by way
of increasing acetylcholine,

200
00:07:44,760 --> 00:07:48,033
and to some extent, increasing
