512
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:21,840
Now why is nicotine present
in potatoes and tomatoes

513
00:20:21,840 --> 00:20:24,150
and in the tobacco plant at all?

514
00:20:24,150 --> 00:20:26,490
Well, nicotine is a plant alkaloid.

515
00:20:26,490 --> 00:20:28,380
We'll get into alkaloids
a little bit later,

516
00:20:28,380 --> 00:20:31,950
but it is thought that these
alkaloids evolved in plants

517
00:20:31,950 --> 00:20:35,970
as a way to prevent
insects from eating them.

518
00:20:35,970 --> 00:20:38,250
And without going into
a lot of insect biology,

519
00:20:38,250 --> 00:20:41,490
the reason or the rationale
behind this explanation is that

520
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:45,240
nicotine is not only a substance
in tobacco that people use

521
00:20:45,240 --> 00:20:47,130
or in the various
medications that people use,

522
00:20:47,130 --> 00:20:50,370
but it's also used as a
pesticide because it can

523
00:20:50,370 --> 00:20:54,030
dramatically disrupt the
nervous system of insects.

524
00:20:54,030 --> 00:20:55,770
It can render them infertile,

525
00:20:55,770 --> 00:20:58,410
which is not to say that it
