526
00:20:58,410 --> 00:20:59,243
We want to say, again,

527
00:20:59,243 --> 00:21:02,340
it is not the case that nicotine
renders humans infertile,

528
00:21:02,340 --> 00:21:04,680
but it can make certain insects infertile.

529
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:06,567
It can actually disrupt
their motor function

530
00:21:06,567 --> 00:21:07,980
and their brain function,

531
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:10,500
and the reasons that it
has such different effects

532
00:21:10,500 --> 00:21:11,940
on insects, in other words,

533
00:21:11,940 --> 00:21:15,810
it can kill them or prevent
them from reproducing,

534
00:21:15,810 --> 00:21:18,750
and therefore explains why
plants probably evolved to have

535
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:20,463
this plant alkaloid, nicotine.

536
00:21:21,430 --> 00:21:22,263
In humans,

537
00:21:22,263 --> 00:21:26,010
because of the differences
in receptors for nicotine,

538
00:21:26,010 --> 00:21:29,276
where they're located, and
the types of receptors,

539
00:21:29,276 --> 00:21:31,380
the effects of nicotine on
humans is quite a bit different.

540
00:21:31,380 --> 00:21:34,020
And again, it does not
cause infertility in humans.

541
00:21:34,020 --> 00:21:36,090
Although I will talk a
